.org/rest/api/2/user?username=trog","name":"trog","emailAddress":"trog@swmud.pl","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Tomasz Welman","active":true},"created":"2009-07-02T05:45:57.340-0500","updated":"2009-07-02T05:45:57.340-0500"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/88771/comment/182278","id":"182278","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=trog","name":"trog","emailAddress":"trog@swmud.pl","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Tomasz Welman","active":true},"body":"Ok. The feature is done. There are no JUnits yet, but they'll come soon.\r\nI'm attaching a patch created with:\r\nsvn diff --diff-cmd /usr/bin/diff -x '-C 3'\r\ncommand from the project root directory. There is also a new file: PosixTarEntry.java.\r\n\r\nTo summarize I've changed private TarEntry members to protected.\r\nCreated PosixTarEntry class, which extends TarEntry. This class is\r\nthen used by TarArchiver, when the appropriate tarLongFileMode was\r\ngiven. There are 2 new modes supported: posix and posix_warn.\r\n\r\n\r\nPlease, tell me what I need to do next, so that my changes will be integrated\r\ninto SVN.","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=trog","name":"trog","emailAddress":"trog@swmud.pl","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure